<p>Creating a new thread for addressing these, as the last thread was getting bloated and was originally posted in 2011. It can be accessed here: <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-378997/complaints-thread">http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-378997/complaints-thread</a></p>
<p>If you have any complaints about the site, please state them here, and we will address them as we can.</p>
<p>Note: This thread is for serious complaints, and trolling/joke complaints will be deleted.</p>
<p>Note 2: This thread is not for complaints about non-staff users. Please message a member of the <a href="http://05command.wikidot.com/disciplinary-main">Disciplinary Committee</a> or a site administrator.</p>

